I meant notI did not mean stammered
Bradshawe.
Our conference is over, sir; and it has a fitting
end, interrupted Alida, haughtily, waving her hand.
I would be alone, Mr. Bradshawe.
Another time, then, when my care for your
welfare, so far as I can study it in these dreary
retreats
,
shall have obliterated these ignominious
suspicions
,
this most ungenerous and unjust
